Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}记忆之扉敞开的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.95,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}你想一同聆听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:04.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\blur1}我便倾诉于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:13.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}啊 虽然这般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:16.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重要的回忆也会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:20.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}被时间之沙掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:24.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而变得暧昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:31.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}说着「命运」这词是如此廉价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:35.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而与我一同开怀大笑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:41.36,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}又是否是我生命中的罗密欧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:46.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大家 一定会将自己的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:49.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}逐渐忘却在心的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}与你的一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:56.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使只有一瞬 也请留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:00.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使成为无法集齐的拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:04.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}那无法寻觅的最后一片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:07.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}记忆之扉敞开的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:09.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}你想一同聆听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:15.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,600)\blur1}我便倾诉于你
